Quattro All-Wheel Drive: Provides exceptional traction and stability in various driving conditions, enhancing cornering performance and confidence on the road.

S-Tronic Dual-Clutch Transmission: Offers quick and seamless gear shifts, contributing to a more engaging driving experience and improved fuel efficiency.

